Problem 01 
  - use http://localhost:3000/api/games/    -- to see all games , paginated if query string with offset and count is provided
  - use http://localhost:3000/api/games/gameID    -- to see all specific game with given ID  
  - Note: All all checking and hardening are also done
problem 02 
  - use http://localhost:3000/api/students/    -- to see all students  
  - use http://localhost:3000/api/students/studentID    -- to see a particular student with given ID  
    - use http://localhost:3000/api/students/studentID/Address    -- to see all addresses of a particular student   
      - use http://localhost:3000/api/students/studentID/Address/AddressID    -- to see a particular address of a particular student given addressId and StudentID
  - Note: All all checking and hardening are also done
Problem 03
  - Title choosen to work as project is : Simple E-Commerce Application
